<MELItem itemNbr="52-11-07" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-52-11-07.1.2-52-11-07_FAA">
<Title>EPAS Disarmed Sensors (*)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="8" nbrRequired="0">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One or more may be inoperative.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>The memo message DOORS MANUAL will be inoperative.  The memo message DOORS AUTO/MANUAL will be displayed if all doors are not in automatic mode (DOORS AUTO displayed).  The associated disarm indication will not be available on the Doors synoptic.  </Para>
<Para>The door 1L flight attendant switch panel MANUAL indicator and the associated passenger door manual mode indicator will be inoperative.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
